    "faq_fFAwqm": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_XEPM9x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is mad honey soap and how is it made?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad Honey Soap is made from the waxy residue of mad honey, which is repurposed into a luxurious, all-natural bathing experience. Infused with coconut oil, olive oil, sunflower oil, and red mud, it offers deep nourishment and gentle exfoliation.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bJtL4k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Does it have side effects on skin?",
            "answer": "<p>Our soap is made from natural ingredients, and most users enjoy its nourishing benefits without side effects. However, we always recommend doing a patch test first to ensure it suits your skin.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_cU9Bya": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do your soaps contain essential oils?",
            "answer": "<p>No, our soaps don’t contain essential oils, they contain carrier oils like coconut and sunflower oil.  Carrier oils are packed with fatty acids that nourish and moisturize your skin. These natural ingredients give you that healthy, youthful glow and feel. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_B7TK9g": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How should I store and care for my soap?",
            "answer": "<p>To make your soap last longer, store it on a well-drained dish between uses. If the bar is too big, feel free to cut it in half for easier handling.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_UzHYFV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are your products tested on animals?",
            "answer": "<p>No, we are committed to cruelty-free practices. None of our products are tested on animals.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6JXXi9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I have sensitive skin, can I use your soap?",
            "answer": "<p>Our soap is made from gentle, natural ingredients, making it suitable for most skin types. If you have sensitive skin, we recommend doing a patch test first.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3UNgd6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use the soap on my face?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, our Mad Honey Soap is gentle enough for use on your face, offering a moisturizing, exfoliating cleanse. Just be sure to patch test first if you're worried about sensitivity.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YjkEjC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is your soap packaged in?",
            "answer": "<p>We use eco-friendly packaging that aligns with our commitment to sustainability. No plastic waste here!<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Gd6WJK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is honey soap suitable for all skin types?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, our Mad Honey Soap is suitable for all skin types, including dry and sensitive skin. Its natural oils and mad honey work to hydrate, protect, and restore your skin.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_P9NyGb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is mad honey soap safe?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, Mad Honey Soap is safe for use. We carefully select natural ingredients to ensure quality and skin compatibility. Always test it on a small area of your skin first. <\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
